   "source": [
    "### 5.2 使用预定义模板\n",
    "\n",
    "系统提供了预定义的偏置模板："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from bias import GRAPH_BIAS_TEMPLATES\n",
    "\n",
    "# 查看可用的模板\n",
    "print(\"可用的图偏置模板:\")\n",
    "for template_name, template in GRAPH_BIAS_TEMPLATES.items():\n",
